<plot>Sparks fly as the viewer is transported behind firelines where the real action is. Crawling down smoky hallways with Engine Company members, cameraman Lou Angeli takes his Betacam where other photographers fear to tread -- down the dragon's throat. No special effects here -- just real, gritty action as firefighters do battle against a stubborn blaze.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653186</url></doc>
